title: Casey Balsham: Cali Trash
description:
Kippy and Foley are in the new studio with guest and good pal Casey Balsham! We're tweaking the audio and some tech stuff so stick with us! Casey talks growing up in California, Chewing Tobacco, and all other sorts of trashy things! Its a classic AYG episode! 


Bonus episodes: www.Patreon.com/AreYouGarbage


Follow Kevin: https://www.instagram.com/kevinryancomedy/


Follow Foley: https://www.instagram.com/foleygrams/


Comedians H. Foley and Kevin Ryan are self proclaimed GARBAGE. Each week a new stand up comedian gets put to the test.


Steal shampoo from hotels?


Own a George Foreman Grill?


Ever worn JNCO Jeans?
